<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM5.6.2">
<l>kaṟkuṅkal vikkellai yilaṉē yeṉṉuṅ kaṟkuṅkalvi yāvēṉum yāṉē yeṉṉuṅ</l>
<l>kaṟkuṅkalvi ceyvēṉum yāṉē yeṉṉuṅ kaṟkuṅkalvi tīrppēṉum yāṉē yeṉṉuṅ</l>
<l>kaṟkuṅkalvic cāramum yāṉē yeṉṉuṅ kaṟkuṅkalvi nātaṉvan tēṟak kolō</l>
<l>kaṟkuṅ kalviyīrk kivaiyeṉ collukēṉ kaṟkuṅ kalviyeṉ makaḷkāṇ kiṉṟaṉavē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>“There is no limit to the learning I learn”, she says,</l>
	<l>“and I am the one who is learnable learning”, she says,</l>
<l>“and I am the one who makes the learnable learning”, she says,</l>
	<l>“and I am the one who ends the learnable learning”, she says,</l>
<l>“and I am all the sap of the learnable learning”, she says,</l>
	<l>while the master of learnable learning settles in [her]?</l>
<l>Why will I say these [words] to you of learnable learning,</l>
	<l>[words also] seen my daughter of learnable learning?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
